            <title>[HBASE-10352] Region and RegionServer changes for opening region replicas, and refreshing store files</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10352</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Region replicas should be opened in read-only mode, and the &quot;replica&quot; mode so that they serve queries from the primary regions&apos; files. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This jira will also capture periodic refreshing of the store files from the secondary regions so that they can get flushed and compacted files according to the &quot;region snapshots&quot; section in the design doc for the parent jira. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
